## 🧠 Key Takeaway Patterns

| Use Case Type      | Ideal Mode | Primary Prompt Focus                                          |
| ------------------ | ---------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| CMF Exploration    | Restyle    | Materials, lighting, emotional tone                           |
| Concept Ideation   | Imagine    | Mood, abstract form, lighting, genre                          |
| Marketing Context  | Background   | Environment, surface, lighting                                |
| Pitch Deck Visuals | All        | Combine Restyle (style), Imagine (vision), Background (context) |

