## 🔧 Qwen Structured Prompt Examples (KeyShot 2026.1)

### Restyle — Seasonal CMF (Structured Format)

```
MATERIALS: brushed bronze case, sand-toned leather strap, warm amber crystal
LIGHTING: golden hour directional light, soft shadow falloff
COLOR: warm bronze, caramel, muted amber, ivory dial
STYLE: luxury product photography, autumn collection aesthetic
QUALITY: high detail, premium surface definition
EXCLUSIONS: no cool tones, no synthetic-looking materials
```

### Imagine — Wellness Brand World (Structured Format)

```
SUBJECT: floating translucent meditation pods
ATTRIBUTES: organic curved forms, semi-transparent shell, interior soft glow
STATE: hovering in still air, serene and dormant
COMPOSITION: wide symmetrical shot, pods arranged in gentle arc
ENVIRONMENT: infinite pale mist void with subtle ground reflection
LIGHTING: soft omnidirectional ambient, warm interior glow per pod
MATERIALS: frosted glass shell, soft-touch matte interior, luminescent membrane
COLOR: pale sage, soft cream, warm peach accents
CAMERA: 35mm moderate depth of field, centered perspective
STYLE: speculative wellness concept art, refined minimalism
QUALITY: atmospheric, high detail, gallery-quality finish
EXCLUSIONS: no hard edges, no mechanical elements, no text, no people
```

### Background — Tech Product Showcase (Structured Format)

```
ENVIRONMENT: clean dark studio platform with subtle reflective surface
LIGHTING: focused overhead softbox, thin rim light from rear right, deep controlled shadows
MATERIALS: matte black acrylic platform, seamless dark gray backdrop, subtle floor reflection
COLOR: deep charcoal, matte black, cool steel accent
STYLE: studio product photography, premium tech aesthetic
QUALITY: crisp, high realism, clean edges
EXCLUSIONS: no clutter, no visible seams, no color cast, no distracting reflections
```

